properties.name: Buckle Bunnies Fund - San Antonio
properties.delivery: Yes, but only to certain areas
properties.contact: DM @bucklebunniesfundtx, text 325-261-6327, or fill out their online Form
properties.details:
Free repro justice bags are available for pick up only.   Each kit contains emergency contraception (plan B).   You can also ask for condoms, lube, NARCAN, painkillers (advil, aleve, ibuprofen), diapers, fentanyl testing strips, pads/tampons, and vbGQY.
 They offer repro, post abortion, and post birth bags.

properties.name: Bridge Collective ATX - Austin
properties.details: Bridge Collective repro kits contain 2 emergency contraception pills (plan B), 2 pregnancy tests, instructions, a few condoms, and information about reproductive health resources in the Central TX area.   Requests are currently limites to 1 delivery per person every 3 months.  If you have any issues with the form, email their volunteer team at deliveryintake@thebridgecollective.org

properties.name: Luz de Atabey Midwifery Project (LAMP) - Austin
properties.details: They do home visits, delivery, and have a weekly pop-up clinic.   They also speak spanish and have interpeters available. All of their services are low cost or free of charge.

properties.name: Dallas Liberation Movement - Dallas
properties.details: To request a kit, text their hotline for support.  Each kit includes: 2 emergency contraception pills (plan B), 2 pregnancy tests, condoms, antacid, a small plastic cup, and an info zine.  They are also always looking for volunteers to help them deliver their repro kits, visit their website to learn more!
